<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id83b5e573-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2" identifier="/us/usc/t41/s132"><num value="132">§ 132.</num><heading> Competitive procedures</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In division B, the term “competitive procedures” means procedures under which an agency enters into a contract pursuant to full and open competition.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id83b5e574-3a70-11f1-ab1a-a784e0a454e2">(<ref href="/us/pl/111/350/s3">Pub. L. 111–350, § 3</ref>, <date date="2011-01-04">Jan. 4, 2011</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/124/3682">124 Stat. 3682</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
